018 so far|publisher=[[Official Charts Company]]|date=5 April 2018|accessdate=1 May 2018}}</ref>\n* WW: 1,400,000<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.org/downloads/GMR2018.pdf|title=Global Music Report 2018|publisher=[[International Federation of the Phonographic Industry]]|accessdate=7 January 2019|page=9}}</ref>\n|\n* BPI: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* ARIA: Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/albums-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Albums|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=5 March 2018|accessdate=3 March 2018}}</ref>\n* GLF: Gold<ref name=\"swedcert\"/>\n* IFPI DEN: Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.dk/?q=content/sam-smith-thrill-it-all-0|title=Certificeringer - Sam Smith - The Thrill of It All|language=Danish|publisher=[[IFPI Denmark]]|accessdate=29 May 2018}}</ref>\n* MC: Platinum<ref name=\"MC\"/>\n* NVPI: Platinum<ref name=\"NVPI\"/>\n* RMNZ: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite certification|region=New Zealand|type=album|artist=Sam Smith|title=The Thrill of It All|recent=website|id=4584|accessdate=25 January 2019}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=row {{TBA|[[Upcoming Sam Smith album|TBA]]}}\n|\n* Scheduled: 2020<ref>https://www.instagram.com/p/B-XD8Vag2Kp/</ref>\n* Label: Capitol\n* Formats: CD, LP, DL\n| colspan=\"12\" {{TBA|To be released}}\n|}\n\n===Remix albums===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:12em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Details\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Lost Tapes \u2013 Remixed]]''\n|\n* Released: 15 May 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Lost-Tapes-Remixed-Sam-Smith/dp/B00WL9XW62/|title=The Lost Tapes - Remixed|publisher=[[Amazon.com]]|accessdate=4 October 2017}}</ref>\n* Label: Kosmo Records\n* Formats: CD, digital download\n|}\n\n==Extended plays==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\"| Title\n! s