 magic in Olympic-inspired beautifully infectious video |last=Lotter |first=Judah Charles |date=16 April 2020 |accessdate=18 April 2020 |website=Meaww}}</ref>}}\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Fire on Fire]]\"\n| 63 || 93 || \u2014 || \u2014 || \u2014 || 38 || 42 || \u2014{{efn|group=upper-alpha|\"Fire on Fire\" did not enter the NZ Top 40 Singles Chart, but peaked at number 13 on the NZ Hot Singles Chart.<ref>{{cite web|url=https://nztop40.co.nz/chart/hotsingles?chart=4578|title=NZ Hot Singles Chart|publisher=Recorded Music NZ|date=31 December 2018|accessdate=28 December 2018}}</ref>}} || 16 || \u2014\n|\n* IFPI DEN: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ifpi.dk/node/8994|title=Sam Smith \"Fire On Fire\"|publisher=IFPI Denmark|date=18 February 2020|accessdate=2 March 2020}}</ref>\n* RIAA: Gold<ref name=\"riaa.com\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Dancing with a Stranger]]\"<br>{{small|(with [[Normani]])}}\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2019\n| 3 || 6 || 8 || 3 || 37 || 4 || 6 || 7 || 3 || 7\n|\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* ARIA: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"ARIA2019\"/>\n* IFPI DEN: Gold<ref>{{cite web|url=http://ifpi.dk/node/8109|title=Sam Smith & Normani \u2013 Dancing with a Stranger|publisher=IFPI Denmark|accessdate=2 April 2019|language=Danish}}</ref>\n* MC: 4\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"cria\"/>\n* RMNZ: Platinum<ref>{{cite certification|region=New Zealand|type=single|artist=Sam Smith and Normani|title=Dancing with a Stranger|recent=website|id=4623|accessdate=20 April 2019}}</ref>\n* RIAA: 3\u00d7 Platinum<ref name=\"RIAA\"/><ref>https://www.instagram.com/p/B-XD8Vag2Kp/</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[How Do You Sleep? (Sam Smith song)|How Do You Sleep?]]\"\n| 7 || 10 || 16 || 14 || 43 || 4 || 7 || 5 || 20 || 24\n|\n* BPI: Platinum<ref name=\"BPI\"/>\n* ARIA: 2\u00d7 Platinum<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.ariacharts.com.au/charts/singles-chart|title=ARIA Australian Top 50 Singles|publisher=[[Australian Recording Industry Association]]|date=25 November 2019|accessdate=23 November