gs of Elton John & Bernie Taupin]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Get Happy (song)|Get Happy]]\" \n| 2019\n| ''[[Judy (soundtrack)|Judy]]''\n|}\n\n==Songwriting credits==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Artist \n! scope=\"col\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Therapy (Mary J. Blige song)|Therapy]]\"\n| rowspan=\"4\"| 2014\n| rowspan=\"4\"| [[Mary J. Blige]]\n| rowspan=\"4\"| ''[[The London Sessions (Mary J. Blige album)|The London Sessions]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Not Loving You\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Right Now (Mary J. Blige song)|Right Now]]\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Nobody But You\"\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Flashlight (Jessie J song)|Flashlight]]\"\n| 2015\n| [[Jessie J]]\n| ''[[Pitch Perfect 2|Pitch Perfect 2: Original Motion Picture Soundtrack]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Freak\"\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2019\n| [[Avicii]]\n| ''[[Tim (Avicii album)|Tim]]''\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"For the Lover That I Lost\"\n| [[Celine Dion]]\n| ''[[Courage (Celine Dion album)|Courage]]''\n|-\n|}\n\n==Music videos==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:20em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\"| Director\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"3\"| As lead artist\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Money on My Mind]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=K0G9T5Bnjlc|title=Sam Smith - Money On My Mind|publisher=[[YouTube]]|accessdate=12 November 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"8\"| 2014\n| rowspan=\"2\"| [[Jamie Thraves]]\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Stay with Me (Sam Smith song)|Stay With Me]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=pB-5XG-DbAA|title=Sam Smith - Stay With Me|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=12 November 2017}}</ref>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Leave Your Lover\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=182TRJq9Zt8|ti