owheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:12em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:18em;\"| Details\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[The Lost Tapes \u2013 Remixed]]''\n|\n* Released: 15 May 2015<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.amazon.com/Lost-Tapes-Remixed-Sam-Smith/dp/B00WL9XW62/|title=The Lost Tapes - Remixed|publisher=[[Amazon.com]]|accessdate=4 October 2017}}</ref>\n* Label: Kosmo Records\n* Formats: CD, digital download\n|}\n\n==Extended plays==\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:10em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"| Details\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"1\"| Peak chart positions\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Billboard 200|US]]<br/><ref name=\"USAlbums\"/>\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| ''[[Nirvana (EP)|Nirvana]]''\n|\n* Released: 4 October 2013 <span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(UK)</span><ref>{{cite web |url=https://itunes.apple.com/gb/album/nirvana-ep/id708375165 |title=Nirvana \u2013 EP by Sam Smith |work=[[iTunes Store]] |accessdate=30 May 2014}}</ref>\n* Label: Capitol\n* Formats: [[Gramophone record|12\"]], digital download\n| 126\n|}\n\n==Singles==\n===As lead artist===\n{| class=\"wikitable plainrowheaders\" style=\"text-align:center;\" border=\"1\"\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:17em;\"| Title\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:1em;\"| Year\n! scope=\"col\" colspan=\"10\"| Peak chart positions\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:13em;\"| [[List of music recording certifications|Certifications]]\n! scope=\"col\" rowspan=\"2\" style=\"width:14em;\"| Album\n|-\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[UK Singles Chart|UK]]<br/><ref name=\"UK\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[ARIA Charts|AUS]]<br/><ref name=\"AUS\"/>\n! scope=\"col\" style=\"width:2.5em;font-size:85%;\"| [[Canadian Hot 100|CAN]]<br/><ref name=\"CANSingl