w\"| \"[[Lay Me Down (Sam Smith song)|Lay Me Down]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=HaMq2nn5ac0|title=Sam Smith - Lay Me Down|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=12 November 2017}}</ref><br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(2015 re-release)</span>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2015\n| Ryan Hope\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"Lay Me Down\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=lvJX7OgPYww|title=Sam Smith - Lay Me Down (Red Nose Day 2015) ft. John Legend|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=12 November 2017}}</ref><br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">([[Red Nose Day 2015|Red Nose Day]] re-release featuring [[John Legend]])</span>\n| Dee Koppang O'Leary\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Writing's on the Wall (Sam Smith song)|Writing's on the Wall]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=8jzDnsjYv9A|title=Sam Smith - Writing's On The Wall (from Spectre)|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=12 November 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Luke Monaghan\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Too Good at Goodbyes]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=J_ub7Etch2U|title=Sam Smith - Too Good At Goodbyes|publisher=YouTube|accessdate=12 November 2017}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| 2017\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[One Last Song]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.promonews.tv/videos/2017/11/30/sam-smith-one-last-song-joe-connor/50799|title=Sam Smith 'One Last Song' by Joe Connor|website=promonews.tv|date=30 November 2017|accessdate=20 April 2020|first=David|last=Knight}}</ref>\n| rowspan=\"2\"| Joe Connor\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Pray (Sam Smith song)#Remix featuring Logic|Pray]]\"<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.promonews.tv/videos/2018/05/11/sam-smith-ft-logic-pray-joe-connor/53060|title=Sam Smith ft Logic 'Pray' by Joe Connor|website=promonews.tv|date=11 May 2018|accessdate=20 April 2020|first=David|last=Knight}}</ref><br/><span style=\"font-size:85%;\">(featuring [[Logic (musician)|Logic]])</span>\n| rowspan=\"3\"| 2018\n|-\n! scope=\"row\"| \"[[Promises (Calvin Harris and Sam Smith song)